* Task 8 fixture: runtime-substitution placeholders in literal targets
* Contains a CALLNAT with a placeholder literal ('PRG&LANG') and a plain literal
* ('PLAINPROG') to verify the downgrade from static to dynamic when & is present.

DEFINE DATA
LOCAL
  1 RESULT-CODE (N2)
END DEFINE

CALLNAT 'PRG&LANG'

CALLNAT 'PLAINPROG'

MOVE 0 TO RESULT-CODE

END
